flowchart TB
U["USERSPACE<br/>agent tries to exec a binary"] ==> SC["execve syscall"]
SC ==> HK["KERNEL · LSM hook<br/>bprm_check_security"]
HK ==> BPF["eBPF program<br/>verified before load (safe)"]
BPF ==> Q{"binary in blocklist?"}
Q ==>|"no"| OK["allow exec"]
Q ==>|"yes"| EP["-EPERM<br/>exec denied"]
EP -.-> N["Backstop: works even if the IDE skips the hook"]

